research/history/round_summaries/round_0079.json:35:      "`lowrank_expert_residual` \u7684 LUTurbo \u5f62\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5e93 + \u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 + \u9759\u6001 residual \u8865\u507f\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u4ecd\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0079.json:38:      "\u6309\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 cost proxy \u4ee3\u7801\u8def\u5f84\u4f30\u7b97\uff0c`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=32 NUM_EXPERTS=64 STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` \u7684\u603b\u6210\u672c\u4e0e r76 \u57fa\u672c\u540c\u91cf\u7ea7\uff0c\u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0079.json:42:      "\u5982\u679c `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` \u660e\u663e\u5f31\u4e8e r76\uff0c\u5219\u53ef\u8f83\u6e05\u6670\u5224\u5b9a\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c `lowrank_expert_residual` \u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u6536\u76ca\u4ecd\u6765\u81ea\u66f4\u5f3a\u7684 residual cleanup\uff0c\u540e\u7eed\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u8003\u8651 `TRUNK_RANK` \u8f74\u6216\u5207\u56de\u5176\u4ed6\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u7ed9 expert stage \u52a0\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0079.json:54:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0079.json:63:    "description": "Round 79 \u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u8ffd routed-only `expert_topk`\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u518d\u6cbf\u5df2\u5931\u6548\u7684 `factorized_expert_topk` \u65b9\u5411\u8ffd\u52a0\u5bbd\u5ea6\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u56de\u5230\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5f3a\u517c\u5bb9\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f family \u505a\u4e00\u��当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1438:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2231:research/history/logs/agent_round_0035.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设：在 EF=1、K=128 的低开销带，lowrank trunk 先吸收平滑主干、expert local top-k 再处理残差，能比 plain expert_topk 与同带宽 plain selector 提供更好的 FVU/total_cost 权衡，并形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 r12->lowrank_expert_topk(K=128) 给出有效信号且 FVU 明显优于当前 0.38x-0.56x 邻域锚点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K 到 160，验证该 family 在 0.69x total_cost 处是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果该原型训练不稳或收益不足，则优先继续实现 `lowrank + expert + residual`，而不是回到 plain topk/jumprelu 的局部扫点。"],"notes_to_memory":["已按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成新 family 接线：`lowrank_expert_topk` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","新增原型 family 的导出形式为 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 静态库约束，兼容性应视为扩展兼容。","已完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`lowrank_expert_topk`, K=128, EF=1 通过。","当前原型采用固定 4 experts、active_experts=1、无新增 tunable 参数，因此本轮只需改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","在 target proxy(1024x4096) 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的估算成本为：K=128 -> total 0.56x；K=160 -> total 0.69x；K=192 -> total 0.81x。低开销起点应优先从 K=128 开始。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
