research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1462:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:715:research/history/logs/agent_round_0048.stdout.log:273:我已经看到 `r47` 只把 FVU 从 `0.13657` 推到 `0.13553`，仍然没过 `<0.5x` 的 `jumprelu` 锚点。下一步我优先判断这是不是 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在当前成本带的结构极限，还是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被错误的运行时路径拦住，避免把 blocker 当成结构结论。
